b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1664,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding Rupie Costs for Agito Weapon Upgrades","message":"<div>Following the balance adjustments of weapons in version 2.0.0, we have modified the rupie costs for upgrading Agito weapons as detailed below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>[Before adjustments]<\/div><div>\\u30fbCrafting a base Agito weapon<\/div><div>2,000,000 rupies<\/div><div>\\u30fbUnbinding a base Agito weapon once (up to four times)<\/div><div>2,000,000 rupies<\/div><div>\\u30fbEnhancing a base Agito weapon<\/div><div>3,000,000 rupies<\/div><div>\\u30fbUnbinding an enhanced Agito weapon<\/div><div>None (An enhanced Agito weapon is fully unbound, so there are no unbinding costs)<\/div><div>\\u30fbTotal cost to craft a fully unbound enhanced Agito weapon<\/div><div>13,000,000 rupies<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>[After adjustments]<\/div><div>\\u30fbCrafting an Agito weapon<\/div><div>2,000,000 rupies<\/div><div>\\u30fbUnbinding a non-refined Agito weapon once (up to four times)<\/div><div>2,000,000 rupies<\/div><div>\\u30fbRefining an Agito weapon<\/div><div>2,500,000 rupies<\/div><div>\\u30fbUnbinding a refined Agito weapon once (up to four times)<\/div><div>7,500,000 rupies<\/div><div>\\u30fbTotal cost to craft a fully unbound refined Agito weapon<\/div><div>42,500,000 rupies<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>As a token of our appreciation for your understanding regarding these adjustments, we are sending the following gifts to all players who started playing until <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1601636400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbAdamantite Ingot x1<\/div><div>\\u30fbExquisite Honey x50<\/div><div>\\u30fbRupies x100,000,000<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>These gifts can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after reception.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1601636400,"prev_article_id":"1659","next_article_id":"1660","image_path":"","update_time":1601636320}}}'